      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' bgcolor='#0E024D' class='spti2'>ORB OF MASTERY</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' class='db'><span class='dbti'>Statistical Information</span><br>
        <b>Classes:</b>&nbsp; Magicians<br>
        <b>Races:</b>&nbsp; Humans, Erudites, Gnomes, Dark Elfs, High Elfs<br>
<b>Type:</b> 1H Blunt<br>
<b>Damage:</b> 20<br>
<b>Delay:</b> 30<br>
        <b>Stats:</b>&nbsp;  +100 MANA +20 INT +15 STR +5 DEX +10 STA +20 SV COLD +20 SV FIRE +10 SV MAGIC<br>
        <b>Special Attributes:</b>&nbsp; MAGIC, NO DROP, LORE<br>
        <b>Slot(s):</b>&nbsp; Primary Hand Slot<br>
        <b>Weight:</b>&nbsp; 1 Stone<br>
        <b>Effect:</b>&nbsp; Manifest Elements (1 Charges)<br>
        &nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' class='db'><span class='dbti'>Acquistion Information</span><br>
        <b>Related Quest:</b> This item is a result of the Mage epic quest<br>
	   </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' class='db'><span class='dbti'>Pricing Information</span><br>
<b>Average cost:</b> Item Not Tradeable<br>	   </td>
    </tr>
	   </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' class='db'><span class='dbti'>Miscellaneous Information</span><br>
        <b>Rarity:</b> Very Rare<br>
        <b>Max Damage:</b> 113<br>
        <b>Damage/Delay Ratio:</b> Destructive (0.666)<br>
        <b>Max Attack Speed:</b> Very Fast (16.666)<br>
        <b>Weapon Performance:</b> Excellent (11.8)<br>
<b>Effect Details:</b>&nbsp; This spell summons an ultimate elemental pet which has a wide variety of attacks. Hits for 67ish, around 3000 hitpoints, casts a 4 to 5 second stun every 12 seconds, and casts a 200 point DD every 6 seconds. <P>Only one pet can be summoned from each Orb.<br>
      </td>
